dct_title_s: Mangroves on the Eastern Coast of Kenya, 2006 (Lines)
dct_description_sm: This line shapefile represents mangroves on the eastern coast of Kenya.
This data was used in Map 6.4 and Map 6.5 in Nature's Benefits in Kenya: An Atlas of Ecosystems and Human Well-Being.
